{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": "I need to create a new MachineConfig resource that configures a custom chrony NTP configuration file on all worker nodes. The file should be placed at /etc/chrony.conf with specific NTP server entries for our internal time servers (time1.corp.example.com and time2.corp.example.com). Please create the MachineConfig YAML following the project's documented patterns and constraints."}, "timestamp": "2026-06-22T21:35:15.210Z"}
